  `kahn(spec, node_set, indeg, [])` and return its result. `kahn/4` deterministically
  peels off zero-in-degree nodes (breaking ties by sorting names), and returns
  `{:error, {:cycle, remaining_tables}}` if a dependency cycle prevents a full ordering.

